snippet.title: Tana Mongeau Corrupting Demi Lovato! Amber Heard: Career Over? Gayle King Not Sorry Over Kobe Drama!
snippet.description:
Tana Mongeau is NOT GOOD NEWS for Demi Lovato! Neither is Machine Gun Kelly! Very concerned for her based on all her recent choices! Also, justice for Johnny Depp! Should Gayle King apologize over her Kobe Bryant mess? Because she's thus far refused to say she's sorry. Jessica Simpson gets revenge - on her father! Do Prince Harry and Meghan Markle have a responsibility to tell the public who's paying for their security? And more of today's hottest headlines, including Lady GaGa, Kim Kardashian, Kesha, Meghan Trainor and MORE! Watch! Enjoy! SHARE!
